{"tid":1551491,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港金融業赤化 4萬億貸款「送中」 有銀行近半借予內地","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T21:42:50.000Z","uid":21592,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1a68642d112f2bef2cc62c92188f3dc28c6ccc64","tid":1551491,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"早於2008年時，東亞客戶總貸款額為2,303億元，當中990億元是內地貸款（佔比43%），79%屬於有抵押；2013年時，4,053億客戶總貸款中，1,798億元為內地貸款（佔比44.4%），抵押比率為70.6%；到2018年客戶貸款總額為5,006億元，內地貸款額為1,850億元（佔比37%），雖然佔比下跌，但抵押比率竟然跌至42.67%，其中一個原因是近乎無底線地向金融企業放貸，300億元貸款額抵押率只得5.7%，遇上壞賬則難有資產可回收。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUTVzVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUTVzVq.jpg&h=49bf3190&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"810c745b2eb563cf21527a21a3f79415f42317c8","tid":1551491,"uid":76310,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強国: 借得到係我本事, 點解要還, 過主啦</span>"},{"pid":"a29d689d609e209be7fec3797df7f12d372be30b","tid":1551491,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:39:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=839cf2ec\" t